<HEADLINE> Ryzhkov Elected as State Duma's First Vice Chairman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Vladimir Ryzhkov, a candidate
nominated by the "Our Home is Russia" parliamentary group, was
elected today as the first vice chairman of Russia's State Duma,
the Itar-Tass news agency reported.
</P>
<P>
Ryzhkov, 31, was vice chairman of the "Our Home is Russia"
parliamentary group. He was nominated by the group to replace
Alexander Shokhin as State Duma's first vice chairman.
</P>
