<HEADLINE> Zhu Rongji Meets Officials Trained on Financial Issues </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier Zhu
Rongji met today with a group of provincial officials who are
currently attending a training course held by the State Institute
of Administration, the Ministry of Finance and the State
Administration of Taxation.
</P>
<P>
