<P>
BEIJING, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Li Tieying, a member of the
Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central
Committee, met here today with a youth delegation from Japan's
Democratic Party led by its deputy leader Kunio Hatoyama.
