<HEADLINE> Arbachakov to Fight Chatchai for WBC Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, September 10 (Xinhua) -- Russian champion Yuri
Arbachakov, who has been out of action due to a fist injury since
last year, is set to fight Thailand's interim champion Chatchai
Dutchboygym for the World Boxing Council (WBC) flyweight title on
November 12.
</P>
