declined 40 cents to end at 3.4 Singapore dollars. OUE Warrant98
fell 33 cents to close at 1.12 dollars. MAA, Roth S. and Singapore
Land lost 30 cents each to finish at 5.25, 6.6, and 7 Singapore
dollars respectively.  
